b8a13f03-f18b-4f1c-90a0-595c8392800d.title: Brother Brace
b8a13f03-f18b-4f1c-90a0-595c8392800d.text:
Hello, <player>. I'm Brother Brace. I'm here to
tell you all about prayer. You can find the prayer
list in your inventory.

196771a9-576a-4e5a-bb6c-6867b8447d12.title: Brother Brace
196771a9-576a-4e5a-bb6c-6867b8447d12.text:
Prayers can help a lot in combat. Click on the
prayer you wish to use to activate it, and click
it again to deactivate it.

c254d92c-dedd-4324-9e17-6b4774a5bf23.title: Brother Brace
c254d92c-dedd-4324-9e17-6b4774a5bf23.text:
Active prayers will drain your Prayer Points, which
you can recharge by finding an altar or other holy spot
and prayer there.

67abbc59-8aee-4e39-b032-17106a219f3f.title: Brother Brace
67abbc59-8aee-4e39-b032-17106a219f3f.text:
As you noticed, most enemies will drop bones when
defeated. Burying bones, by clicking them, will
gain you Prayer experience.

50aa2cee-0758-4549-b448-66a2361cb4f4.title: Brother Brace
50aa2cee-0758-4549-b448-66a2361cb4f4.text:
I'm also the community officer 'round here, so it's my
job to tell you about your friends and ignore list. Which
can also be found in your inventory.

b37d05a6-1769-4b3d-909b-8ce018eea2ef.title: Brother Brace
b37d05a6-1769-4b3d-909b-8ce018eea2ef.text:
I'll tell you a little about each. You can add people to
either list by clicking the add button then typing their
name into the box that appears.

0de11f9e-342a-4637-9989-cc3deade1d65.title: Brother Brace
0de11f9e-342a-4637-9989-cc3deade1d65.text:
You remove people the the lists in the same way. If
you add someone to your ignore list they will not be
able to talk to your or send any form of message to you.

8baf948a-99a0-4c13-acfe-f7af67e24594.title: Brother Brace
8baf948a-99a0-4c13-acfe-f7af67e24594.text:
Your friends list shows the online status of your
friends. Friend in red are offline, friends in green are
online and on the same server and friends in yellow
are online, but on a different server.

dce1cb46-a2e9-4e27-a043-f0b7fc7d75fe.title: <player>
dce1cb46-a2e9-4e27-a043-f0b7fc7d75fe.text: Are there rules on in-game behaviour?

9adacab1-c27f-4a01-a583-5638641e9051.title: Brother Brace
9adacab1-c27f-4a01-a583-5638641e9051.text:
Yes, you should read the rules of conduct on the
website to make sure you do nothing to get yourself
banned.

f273e30f-588a-4aad-b144-0dc81acb72b4.title: Brother Brace
f273e30f-588a-4aad-b144-0dc81acb72b4.text:
But in general, always try to be courteous to other
players - remember the people in the game are real
people with real feelings.

8479ad60-79cc-46f6-8313-2d157ef02fb4.title: Brother Brace
8479ad60-79cc-46f6-8313-2d157ef02fb4.text:
If you go 'round being abusive or causing trouble your
character could end up being the one in trouble.

d38c38cc-e893-4216-abec-292b5bfb728a.title: <player>
d38c38cc-e893-4216-abec-292b5bfb728a.text: Okay, thanks, I'll bear that in mind.

0143a178-e626-4f60-a1d9-5f493dbf833a.title: Brother Brace
0143a178-e626-4f60-a1d9-5f493dbf833a.text: Peace be with you, my child.

options.text: Tell me about my freinds list again.
Nope, I'm ready to move on!

c6dc9947-fb88-40be-b763-675a48bb164d.title: Brother Brace
c6dc9947-fb88-40be-b763-675a48bb164d.text:
Ah, yes, your prayer list. Prayers can help a alot in
combat. Click on the prayer you wish to use to activate
it, and click it again to deactivate it.

4196a4dc-c2fb-4251-8ea4-f661e9ed1783.title: Brother Brace
4196a4dc-c2fb-4251-8ea4-f661e9ed1783.text:
Active prayers will drain your Prayer Points, which
you can recharge by finding an altar or other holy spot
and prayer there.

8060fc4f-8870-45e2-bb76-a86cc464b606.title: Brother Brace
8060fc4f-8870-45e2-bb76-a86cc464b606.text:
As you noticed, most enemies will drop bones when
defeated. Burying bones, by clicking them, will
gain you Prayer experience.

1966df99-bb33-4b01-aec3-d1d3f71d509f.title: Brother Brace
1966df99-bb33-4b01-aec3-d1d3f71d509f.text:
Your friends and ignore lists, yes... I'll tell you a litle
about each. You can add people to either list by clicking
the add button then typing their name into the box that appears.

05e1abed-9a1f-4fdc-8e92-5a83711ea534.title: Brother Brace
05e1abed-9a1f-4fdc-8e92-5a83711ea534.text:
You remove people the the lists in the same way. If
you add someone to your ignore list they will not be
able to talk to your or send any form of message to you.

adfa8de1-955a-46d3-a07a-ac33a629a090.title: Brother Brace
adfa8de1-955a-46d3-a07a-ac33a629a090.text:
Your friends list shows the online status of your
friends. Friend in red are offline, friends in green are
online and on the same server and friends in yellow
are online, but on a different server.
